<font color="yellow">Hati-hati di jalan.</font>

35
00:06:05,196 --> 00:06:06,086
<font color="yellow">Bukannya itu orang?</font>

36
00:06:06,111 --> 00:06:08,131
<font color="yellow">Tunggu.</font>

37
00:06:12,741 --> 00:06:14,251
<font color="yellow">Dia sudah meninggal!</font>

38
