<font color="yellow">Siapa kau?!</font>

56
00:07:43,689 --> 00:07:48,269
<font color="yellow">Hong Nang! Ada perlu apa kemari?</font>

57
00:07:48,269 --> 00:07:52,959
<font color="yellow">Tetua, wanita ini dukun kepala
