92
00:10:57,501 --> 00:10:59,651
<font color="yellow">Kenapa Anda melakukannya?</font>

93
00:11:00,441 --> 00:11:03,431
<font color="yellow">Oh, itu...</font>

94
00:11:04,201 --> 00:11:09,351
