97
00:11:15,761 --> 00:11:17,431
<font color="yellow">Kau itu takut.</font>

98
00:11:17,431 --> 00:11:18,961
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?</font>

99
00:11:18,985 --> 00:11:20,258
<font color="yellow">Ya, kau itu mudah takut.</font>

100
00:11:20,282 --> 00:11:22,282
<font color="yellow">Mudah takut?/
